column2: SELECT TOP # # + cast (p.apstar_id as varchar (#) ) + # + cast (p.apstar_id as varchar (#) ) + # as apstar_id, p.apogee_id, p.ra, p.dec, p.glon, p.glat, p.vhelio_avg, p.vscatter, a.teff, a.logg, a.metals FROM apogeeStar p JOIN aspcapStar a on a.apstar_id = p.apstar_id WHERE ra BETWEEN # AND # AND dec BETWEEN # AND #
